::Feline::

She felt his hands grip her arms and his metal lips press forcefully 
against her own.  She sighed and knew he still wanted her.  That gave 
her the advantage.  She pulled back and looked at him. "I'm happy to 
know that your alright handsome.  But I do need you to put this bot 
(CyberShark) into the CR.  He will come ing useful to you later on."
She smiled evily at HotRod.
